analysis.Summary: This file defines a single-file Vue component that renders an inline SVG graphic of the YouTube logo.
analysis.Purpose: Provides a reusable YouTube social media icon for use throughout the application’s UI.

Components.name: YouTubeIcon
responsibilities: Render an SVG path describing the YouTube logo
Expose no reactive data or props (purely presentational)

Notes: No <script> or <style> blocks—component is purely declarative SVG markup.
Uses a CSS custom property (--white) for fill color, so theming depends on that variable being defined.
Fixed width and height (21×14) may need adaptation for responsive layouts or scaling via parent CSS.
Consider adding accessibility attributes (role="img" or aria-label) if required by design guidelines.
